# Rust
/target/
/lib*.rlib
apps/desktop/src-tauri/target/
apps/desktop/src-tauri/gen/*
!apps/desktop/src-tauri/gen/android/
!apps/desktop/src-tauri/gen/android/**

# Node
node_modules/

# Build / distribution artifacts
dist/
apps/web/dist/
*.tar.gz

# Orchestration scratch (not part of the shipped repo)
.orchestration/

# Local environment / secrets
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
# ...except the two committed Compose defaults, which hold no secrets: they only
# pin COMPOSE_PROFILES=single-node so a bare `docker compose up` selects exactly
# one app service. Put local-only values in .env.local instead (still ignored).
!/.env
!/docker/.env

# Logs and OS cruft
*.log
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
SPEC-COVERAGE.md
# Per-executor cargo target dirs (agents build in their own to avoid lock contention)
/target-*
# Scratch coverage snapshots taken while measuring
/apps/web/coverage-*
/Projectschancelatarget-tcmeasure
/Projectschancelatarget-t14
